\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af85c33bc2d28bfafffe9bfd11fa792fb0c0035c","tid":632120,"uid":80241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"所以永遠要為自己打算。<br />\n係事業方面，自己銀行戶口方面<br />\n我就係過來人，曾經分手都遇過師兄你既痛<br />\n到而加慢慢長大，知道愛情唔可以當飯食，<br />\n所以我不斷增值自己，賺更多錢。<br />\n可能你地覺得只有錢 好膚淺，<br />\n但錢真正可以保護到自己，愛情只係你人生路上既一小部分。<br />\n港女搵到個有錢男朋友就飛左原本男朋友，所以樓主你要增值好自己，等另一半搵唔到一個飛你既理由"},{"pid":"7ca4c02eb767abc25c1aeeb15b523abf51781474","tid":632120,"uid":88884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:04:43.000Z","msg":"唔通真係人會變 情會厭 從沒什麼保險？<br />\n段感情你投入過 另一半唔想都無辦法 勉強無幸福<br />\nLife must go on ! 共勉之"},{"pid":"1bd2b8c863f5441595e3baf3d331b166328b28ea","tid":632120,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:15:11.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e05b7c4cce8a38eb3a7edf86cee34c02c6fc6f","tid":632120,"uid":111625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0298b0173509a0a43aee274cbe5e0d6f5b94e220","tid":632120,"uid":77769,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:21:45.000Z","msg":"完全同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8789d8e8f0f73579c3af62c5a9c798be5014c99","tid":632120,"uid":111625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:30:00.000Z","msg":"巴打加油,好多同路人,我岩岩過左一個月<br />\n仲知道對方同第二個開心緊,真係好痛<br />\n但明明自己都冇做錯,點解會搞成咁<br />\n當對方搵到第二個/唔愛既時候,真係可以是但一個理由收你皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07564244102b8ec9bcbf520f4f1e1ce38979398","tid":632120,"uid":89941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim